	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you fish in Cabilis, you catch things like &quot;13 pound bass&quot; and &quot;7 pound bass&quot;.&nbsp;&nbsp;The weight on them is consistently one-tenth of their stated weight, so the 13 pound bass weighs 1.3, and the 7 pounder weighs .7.  Thus, it can be assumed that EQ weights are in tens of pounds.  So, yes, a weakling wizard with a 55 Strength, can carry 550 pounds of loot and gear before he even begins to walk slowly.  And, yes, a &quot;stone&quot; is a 14 pound weight.  They still use it for weighing horses and jockeys in the real world.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
